all our tire pressure gauges are for export purpose selling to more than 20 foreign countries, winning an unanimous trust from the users in the united states, japan and europe, who have offered us a status of their designated manufacturer of such gauges under their brand name. presently we yearly produce more than 3 million different pressure gauges and more than 10 million pen-type pressure gauges and is listed among the key export commodity manufacturers at the municipal level. since 1986 our company has been confirmed as a contract-respectful and high credit enterprise. 

our company was founded in 1986. with full assistance and concern of friends from different walks it has grown into a medium-sized modern enterprise with a built space of 3000m',more than 10 million yuan-worthy fixed assets and more than 200 employees (including more than 20 technical experts). this is a result of over 10 years of our struggles.

		is an international manufacturer specializing in designing, developing & 
		producing pressure gauges (manometer, pressure meter) since 1980, with iso9001 approval, over 800 different items have 
		been manufactured, including: standard dry 
		pressure gauge, 
		liquid filled pressure gauge, freon pressure 
		gauge, capillary pressure gauge (hydrometer), compound and 
		vacuum pressure gauge, acetylene and oxygen pressure gauge, 
		all stainless steel pressure gauges, spiral gauges and fire 
		gauge, oxygen medical gauge, the monthly production capability at 
		present has reached 
    	250,000 pcs. 

		as our products , we do classify for our pressure gauges by some main 
		subjects for various industries, 1' to 4' gauges, vacuum gauges to high 
		pressure gauges(10000psi) .
		we can also build custom, world-class quality gauges for oem 
		applications.
		as a producer for gauges, we do business always with honest and 
		reliable, i can't tell you we are the leader manufacturer in the gauge 
		field, but, i can tell you, you find us, you just find a reliable source 
		for pressure gauges.so, may we suggest that you write us when you find out the pressure 
		gauge you are looking for, we look forward to the pleasure of serving 
		you soon.











some of our products: 
		miniature pressure gauges, vacuum gauges, 
		all stainless steel pressure gauges, are very good sell in market.

    	engineered to withstand 300% full scale pressure without rupture of the 
		bourdon tube, 130% full scale pressure without loss of accuracy, and a 
		lifetime warranty makes nf pressure gauges the exception in the 
		marketplace today. but it really doesn't cost more to use nf gauges. 
		it's economical!
